data.description: Welcome to this recently updated 3 bed 2 bath home on 2.4 acres in Spencer County! This home features a large living room with a floor to ceiling brick fireplace, an updated kitchen with a tray ceiling, and a dining room. Off to the left side of the house you have a secondary full bath, 2 secondary rooms, and an added on primary suite with a large walk in closet, large bedroom and full bathroom! Outside you have a nice concrete patio that's fenced in, a front porch to watch the cars go by, and a large detached garage! The garage has its own electric meter, and has some great old furniture and items inside that remain with the home! at the back of this large 2.4 acre lot there is a pond. All of this and just minutes to Taylorsville, Mt. Washington! Boundaries shown are approximate.
